title: $:/plugins/flibbles/relink-titles/readme

Highly customizable relinking of tiddler titles //related// to the renamed tiddler.

* Rename a hierarchy of subtiddlers when renaming a root tiddler.
* Rename related settings tiddlers, such as `$:/prefix/MyTiddler` when renaming `MyTiddler`.
* Whatever else you want, so long as you can build a filter for it.

See <a href={{$:/plugins/flibbles/relink-titles!!source}}>the tw5-relink website</a> for more details and examples.
